o-haye-poster>[https://www.amazon.co.uk/Klitschko-REPRODUCTION-BOXING-PROMO-Poster/dp/B00CON01LE Klitschko VS HAYE REPRODUCTION BOXING PROMO PHOTO Poster 40 x 30 cm]</ref>}}\n|{{center|500,000,000}}\n|<ref name=\"Haye can silence his critics with a knockout showing\">{{cite news|url=http://sport360.com/article/other/boxing-mma/156153/fight-club-david-haye-can-silence-his-critics-with-a-knockout-showing-against-mark-de-mori/|title=Fight Club: Haye can silence his critics with a knockout showing|date=11 January 2016|accessdate=26 August 2017|publisher=Sport360}}</ref><ref name=\"Mayweather v McGregor could happen\">{{cite news|url=http://www.dublinlive.ie/sport/other-sport/mayweather-v-mcgregor-could-happen-11340119|title=Mayweather v McGregor could happen, claims David Haye|date=16 May 2016|accessdate=26 August 2017|publisher=Dublin Live}}</ref><ref name=\"David Haye to Retire\">{{cite news|url=http://www.boxingscene.com/david-haye-retire-i-know-if-i-fight-again--41086|title=David Haye to Retire? - I Don't Know If I Will Fight Again|date=3 July 2011|accessdate=26 August 2017|publisher=boxingscene.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2014|November|15|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Kubrat Pulev]]\n|{{center|''Showdown In Hamburg''}}\n|{{center|300,000,000}}\n|<ref name=\"pulevworld1\"/><ref name=\"pulevworld2\"/><ref name=\"pulevworld3\"/>\n|-\n!\n! Total viewership\n!\n! 800,000,000\n!\n|}\n\n=== Germany ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Date !! Fight !! Billing<ref name=\"eyeonthering\">{{cite web |title=Wladimir Klitschko Fights in the Vault |url=https://eyeonthering.com/fighters/wladimir-klitschko |website=Eye On The Ring |accessdate=March 11, 2020}}</ref> !! Viewership ({{abbr|avg.|average}}) !! Network !! Source(s)\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|1999|September|25|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Axel Schulz]]\n|{{center|''Klitschko vs. Schulz''}}\n|{{center|11,200,000}}\n|RTL Television\n|<ref name=schulz>[https://www.boxing247.com/news/Vladimir-Klitschko-Profile.php Wladimir Klitschko Profile - East Side Boxing]</ref><ref name=schulz1>[https://www.focus.de/panorama/boulevard/entertainment-brueder-bumm_aid_178789.html Die Schwergewichtsboxer Vitali und Wladimir Klitschko \u00fcber Hiebe, Geld und den Showdown in Las Vegas] (ger.)</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|1999|December|4|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. Lajos Eros\n|{{center|''Klitschko vs. Eros''}}\n|{{center|7,010,000}}\n|Sat.1\n|<ref name=eros>[https://www.presseportal.de/pm/6708/126925 Vitali Klitschko vs. Chris Byrd generates 9,79 million viewers, breaking the station's record held by Wladimir (German)]</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2000|October|14|format=dmy}}}}\n|[[Chris Byrd vs. Wladimir Klitschko]]\n|{{center|''Revenge Of The Brother''}}\n|{{center|9,390,000}}\n|[[Sat.1]]\n|<ref name=byrd1>[https://rp-online.de/sport/wladimir-klitschko-ist-weltmeister_aid-8228603 Wladimir Klitschko is the new world champion (German)]</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2003|March|8|format=dmy}}}}\n|[[Wladimir Klitschko vs. Corrie Sanders]]\n|{{center|''The Next Big Thing''}}\n|{{center|9,150,000}}\n|[[ZDF]]\n|<ref name=sanders>[https://www.moz.de/sport/sport/artikel-ansicht/dg/0/1/1763975/ (German) Boxen kehrt nach neun Jahren ins ZDF zur\u00fcck]</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2003|August|30|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Fabio Eduardo Moli]]\n|{{center|''Night Of The Giants''}}\n|{{center|7,630,000}}\n|ZDF\n|\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2003|December|20|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Danell Nicholson]]\n|{{center|''Klitschko vs. Nicholson''}}\n|{{center|7,920,000}}\n|[[ZDF]]\n|\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2005|April|23|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Eliseo Castillo]]\n|{{center|''Klitschko vs. Castillo''}}\n|{{center|6,440,000}}\n|Das Erste\n|\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2006|April|24|format=dmy}}}}\n|[[Chris Byrd vs. Wladimir Klitschko II]]\n|{{center|''Revenge Is The Name Of The Game''}}\n|{{center|10,170,000}}\n|[[Das Erste]]\n|<ref name=byrd2>[https://www.dwdl