er|''Alle G\u00fcrtel. Ein Champion''}}\n|{{center|12,260,000}}\n|RTL Television\n|<ref name=mormeck>[http://boxrec.com/media/index.php/Wladimir_Klitschko_vs._Jean-Marc_Mormeck Wladimir Klitschko vs. Jean-Marc Mormeck]</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2012|July|7|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Tony Thompson (boxer)|Tony Thompson]] II\n|{{center|''Hard Rocks''}}\n|{{center|8,360,000}}\n|RTL Television\n|<ref name=thompson2>[https://www.derwesten.de/sport/ueber-acht-millionen-zuschauer-sehen-klitschko-sieg-id6855661.html Klitschko's win generates 41,5% market share (German)]</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2012|November|10|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Mariusz Wach]]\n|{{center|''Battle Of The Giants''}}\n|{{center|11,770,000}}\n|RTL Television\n|<ref name=wach>[https://www.sports.ru/tribuna/blogs/innalagun/461927.html TV ratings for Klitschko vs Pianeta and Klitschko vs Wach]</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2013|May|4|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Francesco Pianeta]]\n|{{center|''Showtime In Mannheim''}}\n|{{center|8,310,000}}\n|RTL Television\n|<ref name=wach/>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2013|October|7|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Alexander Povetkin]]\n|{{center|''Klitschko vs. Povetkin''}}\n|{{center|11,020,000}}\n|RTL Television\n|<ref name=povetkin>[http://sport.bigmir.net/boks/profi/1596302-Boj-Klichko---Povetkin-sobral-rekordnye-telerejtingi-v-Ukraine-i-Rossii Klitschko vs. Povetkin: TV audience in Ukraine, Russia and Germany] (rus.)</ref><ref name=povetkin1>[https://www.ksta.de/quotenduell--klitschko-schlaegt-schwachen-lanz-klar-5311668 TV numbers: Klitschko easily defeats Markus Lanz] (ger.)</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2014|April|26|format=dmy}}}}\n|Wladimir Klitschko vs. [[Alex Leapai]]\n|{{center|''Can{{'}}t Stop''}}\n|{{center|9,000,000}}\n|RTL Television\n|<ref name=leapai>[https://www.sportsnews24.com/boxing-mma/klitschko-leapai-does-9-million-viewers-on-german-rtl-network/ Klitschko-Leapai does 9 million viewers on German RTL ne