loth.org/index.html Beth Oloth, Jerusalem]\n*[[Beth Jacob Jerusalem]]\n*[http://www.bnoschana.org/index.htm Bnos Chana, Beit Shemesh]\n*[http://bnottorah.com/  Bnot Torah Institute, Jerusalem]\n*[http://emuna.ac.il/ Emunah College of Education]\n*[http://www.emunahtorahart.org/ Emunah Torah Art]\n*[http://sephardicseminary.org/  Eshel Sephardic Women's Seminary]\n*[[EYAHT|Eyaht College for Women]]\n*[http://www.midrashot.org/ Igud HaMidrashot]\n*[http://shiratdevorah.org/ Midrasha Shirat Devora]\n*[http://www.navehadasa.com/ Neve Hadassah for Women]\n*[http://www.nevey.org/index.php Neve Yerushalaym College]\n*[[Nishmat (midrasha)|Nishmat, Jewish Center for Women]]\n*[http://www.matan.org.il/eng/ Maatan HaSharon]\n*[http://www.machal.michlalah.edu/ Machal Michlalah]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20081229054609/http://www.machonalte.com/ Machon Alte Chabad]\n*[http://www.machonmaayan.org/  Machon Maayan Program]\n*[http://www.mayanot.edu/  Mayanot Women's Learning Program]\n*[http://www.diaspora.org.il/roni.html Machon Roni, Jerusalem]\n*[http://www.msy.org.il/ Machon Shoshanat Yerushalaym]\n*[[Tal Institute|Machon Tal, Givat Shaul, Jerusalem]]\n*[http://www.maayanotsem.com/ Maayanot Sem]\n*[http://www.mevaseret.org/mmy/index.php Michlelet Mevaseret Yerushalaym]\n*[http://midrasha.biu.ac.il/en/ Midrasha Bar Ilan Advanced Torah Studies]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20071227100752/http://www.efrata.ac.il/ Midrasha Efrata]\n*[http://www.michlalah.edu/  Midrasha Michlalah]\n*[http://www.talpiot.ac.il/  Midrasha Talpiot]\n*[http://www.midreshetakko.net/ Midreshet Akko]\n*[http://www.midreshetamit.org/default.asp Midreshet Amit]\n*[[Midreshet Aviv]]\n*[http://www.shaveihevron.org/show_item.asp?levelId=62387 Midreshet Shirat Hevron]\n*[http://www.batzion.co.il/ Midreshet Bat Tzion]\n*[http://berotbatayin.org/  Midreshet Berot Bat Ayin]\n*[http://www.mbinat.co.il/English Midreshet Binat]\n*[http://www.midreshetdevora.org/index.htm Midreshet Devora Center]\n*[http://www.midrasha.co.il/eng/default.asp Midreshet Ein Ha Natziv]\n*[http://www.miemunah.org/ Midreshet Emunah]\n*[[Midreshet HaRova]]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20081004183355/http://www.mhebron.org/  Midreshet Hebron]\n*[http://www.midreshetmoriah.com/torah/questions.asp Midreshet Moriah]\n*[[Midreshet Lindenbaum]]\n*[http://www.darchenoam.org/mrc-approach-to-learning/ Midreshet Rachel Shapell's]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20070717030243/http://www.shuva.org/ Midreshet Shuva]\n*[http://www.midreshet-tel-hai.co.il/ Midreshet Tel Hai]\n*[http://www.midreshettehillah.org/MT10a/index.html Midreshet Tehilla, Yerushalaym]\n*[http://www.tzvia.org/  Midreshet Tzvia, Yerushalaym]\n*[http://www.midreshet-yeud.org.il/eng/  Midreshet Yeud, Jerusalem]\n*[http://www.orchaya.org.il/english/  Ohr Chaya Center, Jerusalem]\n*[http://www.orothagalil.org/ Orot HaGalil College]\n*[http://www.schooly2.co.il/pelech_jer/page.asp?page_parent=63881 Pelech School Jerusalem]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20090103065555/http://www.pninim.org/ Pninim Kiryat Moshe]\n*[http://shaanan.ac.il/ Shaanan Academic Religious Teachers' College]\n*[http://www.shareibina.com/  Sharei Bina Women's Center]\n*[http://www.shaalvim.org/sfw/  Shalvim Midrasha for Women]\n*[http://www.shearim.com/ Shearim College for Women]\n*[http://www.msy.org.il/ Shoshanat Yerushalaym]\n*[http://www.tiferetcenter.com/  Tiferet Center Beit Shemesh]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20081119064655/http://www.tomerdevorah.net/main.htm Tomer Devorah Seminary]\n*[http://www.yta.org.il/girls/ Torah Academy for Girls]\n*[http://toratreva.org/Joomla/index.php Torah Reva Yerushalaym]\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Israeli Hebrew schools==\n*[http://acelearning.co.il/ Ace Academic Center]\n*[http://www.beitmargalit.com/en/ Beit Margalit Hebrew School]\n*[http://www.democratics.org.il/ Democratic School of Hadera]\n*[http://keren.torahindex.com/default.asp?iId=HILHG Keren HaYeled Hebrew School]\n*[http://www.nachalnovea.com/KiryatBreslev/GanYehudit/gan